00:52:53,295 --> 00:52:55,002
Tembak kepala mereka.

454
00:53:19,196 --> 00:53:20,903
Bidik.

455
00:53:22,366 --> 00:53:24,027
Tarik.

456
00:53:26,286 --> 00:53:28,027
Ulangi.

457
00:53:29,540 --> 00:53:33,750
Bidik, tarik, ulangi.

458
00:54:30,809 --> 00:54:33,972
Aku melihatmu, dasar--

459
00:54:38,358 --> 00:54:39,689
Elvis!

460
00:54:39,777 --> 00:54:40,892
Kau di telepon juga?

461
00:54:42,571 --> 00:54:44,733
- Apa?
