462
00:54:44,823 --> 00:54:46,939
Ya. Gadis itu.

463
00:54:47,159 --> 00:54:50,493
Dr. Ashford tak bilang
ada kesepakatan dengan orang lain.

464
00:54:50,579 --> 00:54:52,115
Aku rasa kita rekan.

465
00:54:58,378 --> 00:54:59,413
Sial.

466
00:55:26,615 --> 00:55:28,572
Angela?

467
00:55:30,536 --> 00:55:32,823
Semua akan baik-baik saja.

468
00:55:33,580 --> 00:55:35,491
Tidak perlu takut.

469
00:55:38,418 --> 00:55:40,079
Kau akan kami antar pulang.

470
00:55:43,590 --> 00:55:44,580
Astaga.

471
00:55:50,389 --> 00:55:51,424
Tolong!

472
00:56:08,282 --> 00:56:09,272
Terri?

473
00:56:28,844 --> 00:56:32,883
Kau tidak bisa menolongnya. Tak bisa lagi.

474
00:56:35,517 --> 00:56:37,224
Aku melihat perbuatan mereka.

475
00:56:38,353 --> 00:56:40,060
- Apa kau Angela?
- Ya.

476
00:56:40,981 --> 00:56:43,598
Kita harus bergegas
sebelum mereka kembali.

477
00:56:45,360 --> 00:56:46,395
Pegang ini.

478
00:56:52,743 --> 00:56:54,825
Angela Ashford, ya?

479
00:56:54,912 --> 00:56:57,370
Itu nama dewasa untuk gadis kecil.

480
00:56:57,539 --> 00:56:58,904
Aku bukan gadis kecil.

481
00:56:59,875 --> 00:57:04,085
- Semua temanku memanggilku Angie.
- Angie?

482
00:57:06,256 --> 00:57:07,291
Aku suka itu.

483
00:57:12,346 --> 00:57:13,882
Mereka ada di sini.

484
00:57:13,972 --> 00:57:16,885
Tak apa. Mereka lamban.
Kita bisa lewati mereka.

485
00:57:17,351 --> 00:57:19,809
Tidak. Bukan mereka.

486
00:57:21,772 --> 00:57:22,762
Mereka.

487
00:57:26,610 --> 00:57:27,600
Mundur.

488
00:57:54,846 --> 00:57:56,712
Jangan gerak.

489
00:57:57,307 --> 00:57:58,923
Kurasa kau butuh bantuan.

490
00:57:59,142 --> 00:58:01,349
- Kau kerja untuk Umbrella?
- Dulu.

491
00:58:01,770 --> 00:58:07,732
Sampai kami ditinggal mati di sini.
Aku menganggap diri ku pekerja lepas.

492
00:58:09,361 --> 00:58:12,729
Sersan Nicholai Genovev, siap melayani.

493
00:58:15,033 --> 00:58:16,740
- Ayo!
- Tunggu! Angie!

494
00:58:16,994 --> 00:58:19,326
Selamatkan dia! Aku bisa atasi ini.

495
00:58:28,714 --> 00:58:29,795
Sial.

496
00:58:38,015 --> 00:58:40,347
Mulai sekarang, tetap disampingku.

497
00:58:41,810 --> 00:58:42,800
KELUAR

498
00:58:42,894 --> 00:58:44,225
Terhalang.

499
00:58:45,689 --> 00:58:47,225
Bagaimana sekarang?

500
00:58:59,953 --> 00:59:03,446
Tunggu di sini. Waspadalah, paham?

501
01:00:15,112 --> 01:00:15,943
SELlMUT APl

